{"tid":355094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸女子滑倒跌落熔岩中片瘋傳,官媒紛闢謠　網民:你有什麼資格批判造謠者","createTime":"2017-08-11T04:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T12:52:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f12d73c3d50086438607b72d746f8a0d4b869f00","tid":355094,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fire-01_aRN0S_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffire-01_aRN0S_1200x0.png&h=15f65b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%BB%91%E5%80%92%E8%B7%8C%E8%90%BD%E7%86%94%E5%B2%A9%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E7%B4%9B%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E6%89%B9%E5%88%A4%E9%80%A0%E8%AC%A0%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25BB%2591%25E5%2580%2592%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E7%2586%2594%25E5%25B2%25A9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%25B4%259B%25E9%2597%25A2%25E8%25AC%25A0-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A4%25E9%2580%25A0%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=z4mDHYM5U6lFCLixjcIXVcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ab7e9e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25BB%2591%25E5%2580%2592%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E7%2586%2594%25E5%25B2%25A9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%25B4%259B%25E9%2597%25A2%25E8%25AC%25A0-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A4%25E9%2580%25A0%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%2580%2585%2F&h=210c0abc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%BB%91%E5%80%92%E8%B7%8C%E8%90%BD%E7%86%94%E5%B2%A9%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E7%B4%9B%E9%97%A2%E8%AC%A0-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E6%89%B9%E5%88%A4%E9%80%A0%E8%AC%A0%E8%80%85/</a><br />\n大陸近日廣傳一段短片，指七月中旬大陸某旅行團組織遊客來到美國一著名火山口參觀，有年輕男女遊客不顧警示，擅自越過警戒線拍照，當中一名不慎滑倒跌落熔岩中，「頃刻間化作一縷青煙灰飛煙滅」。該短片今日獲《人民日報》、《環球時報》、《共青團中央》等在社交媒體轉載闢謠，指片段原是經過後期製作而成，原片段其實是在海邊，是一名女子在海邊的岩岸不慎滑倒。<br />\n<br />\n有大陸網民則在人民網的帖下揶揄：「你有什麼資格批判造謠者，論造謠，你們才是宗師和集大成者。」亦有網民指，「這特效完爆某些電視劇！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-JsYqemHkvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-JsYqemHkvs&d=z4mDHYM5U6lFCLixjcIXVcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f9c9f15a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-JsYqemHkvs</a>"},{"pid":"3255fd0c0dcbbbb1a9f049c79d4aefbecfc27527","tid":355094,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac423869e2c6996e3e5c6e1aafe8114b7594dbf","tid":355094,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"點解唔係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323a72b4eee13576c126f08e691e19a65a4a578e","tid":355094,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58678a231db8fee84d1c2843092646b65f776d56","tid":3550